Malaria Forecasting System
Developer: Kaushik Sarkar (drkaushiksarkar)

This software is developed to support climate-informed early warning surveillance, prediction, and decision-making.

If you use this software, model, or methodology in your research or publication, please cite it as follows:

---
CITATION:
Sarkar, K. (2025). *Malaria Forecasting System: A Streaming Inference and Adaptive Fine-Tuning Framework*. GitHub repository: https://github.com/drkaushiksarkar/malaria-forecasting-system
---

